verbose_text: Little is known about Asb3, but Chung et al. reported that Asb3 is a negative regulator of cellular responses to TNF-alpha by ubiquitination and proteasome mediated degradation of tumor necrosis factor receptor II (TNF-R2) [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: TNF-alpha by ubiquitination and proteasome-mediated degradation of tumor necrosis factor receptor
